#"Added Custom4" = Table.AddColumn(#"Removed Columns1", "Major Appeal Code", each "NA")
```

This hardcodes `Major Appeal Code = "NA"` for every row.

So this is a required output field in the BC layout, but there is currently no dynamic source logic behind it.

