## Add line number

```m
#"Added Index" = Table.AddIndexColumn(#"Renamed Columns8", "Index.1", 0, 1, Int64.Type)
#"Renamed Columns9" = Table.RenameColumns(#"Reordered Columns11",{{"Index.1", "Line No."}})
```

This creates a sequential **`Line No.`** column starting at 0.

### Business meaning

This is likely required by the target journal import format to uniquely order or identify rows.

